 These are inputted into a mathematical formula, and the resulting number would be the code for the attack strategy. This formula will only work if all the six generals input their pair correctly. Otherwise, they would get a gibberish number for which there's no attack strategy. <br/><br/>

Now, even if one or two generals are compromised. They won't be able to reconstruct code for the attack strategy themselves. <br/><br/>

